repo_description: A Fortnite database app, for checking weapons and items.

schemas.name: schema.graphql
schemas.content:
type Query {
    fortniteweaponsfiltername(query: String): [Weapon!]!
    fortniteweaponsfiltertype(query: String): [Weapon!]!
    fortniteweaponsfilterweapontype(query: String): [Weapon!]!
    fortniteweaponsfilterweaponitemrarity(query: String): [Weapon!]!
}

type Weapon {
    id: ID!
    name: String!
    type: String!
    weaponType: String!
    itemRarity: String!
    img: String!
    information: [Info!]!
}

type Info {
    damage: Int!
    critialHitChance: String!
    critialHitDamage: String!
    fireRate: Float!
    magazineSize: Int!
    range: Int!
    durabilty: String!
    reloadTime: String!
    ammoCost: Int!
    impact: Float!
}
